g?v=1690795783 320w" width="1200" height="800" alt="Discover your niche through train the trainer - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Discover your niche through train the trainer - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" style="aspect-ratio:1200 / 800" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jOxtWs ffIUiZ pf-25_"/><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-26_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-28_">As a trainer, your expertise will shine brightest when you focus on a niche that aligns with your passions and strengths. Take the time to explore different fields and identify the area where your knowledge and experience can add the most value.<br><br>Whether it's first aid, technology, fitness, leadership, wellness, or any other subject, finding your niche is the foundation for success in training.
